oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Opryland Music Demo Recordings - Y-69
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording is of a group of demo recordings from Opryland Music. Recordings are from an unknown date and recorded by an unknown band. Recording changes from Digital Audio Tape sessions between the recordings of "Uninvited Memory" and"Truly I Love Thee."
